"""Test get_wlp_information success."""
with mock.patch.object(self.wlp.common, 'get_resource', return_value=self.
    data.wlp_info) as mck_wlp_info:
    wlp_info = self.wlp.get_wlp_information(self.data.array)
    self.assertEqual(self.data.wlp_info, wlp_info)
    mck_wlp_info.assert_called_once_with(category='wlp', resource_level=
        'symmetrix', resource_level_id=self.data.array)
